Package org.jasr.currentcy.config

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationConfig
    Standard application configuration including all Spring specific infrastructure such as scheduling, component scanning, properties files and such
    DatasourceConfig
    Datasource configuration for production.
    EmailConfig
    Email configuration, externalized to a properties file.
    PersistenceConfig
    Persistence configuration in the immediately superior level to Datasource configuration.
    SwaggerConfig
    Swagger configuration for the application.
    WebAppInitializer
    The center of the Spring MVC configuration.
    WebMvcConfig
    Web configuration for Spring MVC, including component scan for web components such as controllers.
